{
  "text": "\u2022 In many countries, co-payments are used and different levels of payment for different services can modify how people use services, [CITATION_1] and, in the NHS, the length of time people have to wait to see different healthcare providers can have a similar effect.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "205081926"
